OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FEvents are being held to mark the 20th
OL,7,Fanniversary of the Royal Regiment of
OL,8,FScotland, with one senior officer
OL,9,Fsaying it is an opportunity to
OL,10,Frecognise "everyone who has served
OL,11,Fwith us".
OL,13,FThe regiment was formed on March 28
OL,14,F2006, from six of Scotland's historic
OL,15,Finfantry regiments, as part of a wider
OL,16,Frestructuring of the British military
OL,17,Fimplemented by the then Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
