PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FIt is Scotland's only infantry
OL,7,Fregiment and the senior line infantry
OL,8,Fregiment in the British Army, and
OL,9,Fdraws its members from communities
OL,10,Facross Scotland and beyond.
OL,12,FSince its formation, it has been one
OL,13,Fof the most active regiments in the
OL,14,FBritish Army, with deployments to
OL,15,FIraq, Afghanistan and Bosnia,
OL,16,Falongside more recent Nato commitments
OL,17,Fin Europe and the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FToday, its troops continue to play a
OL,7,Fleading role in major international
OL,8,Fexercises and hold high-readiness
OL,9,Fcommitments, including in Cyprus,
OL,10,Fwhere they stand ready to deploy
OL,11,Fwithin hours across Europe, the Middle
OL,12,FEast and Africa.
OL,14,FAs well as overseas postings, the
OL,15,Fregiment has also played an important
OL,16,Frole at home, with troops supporting
OL,17,Fcommunities during flooding, wildfires
OL,18,Fand the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
