PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FTo mark two decades since its
OL,7,Fformation, soldiers from the regiment
OL,8,Fformed the number "20" with torches at
OL,9,FGlencorse Barracks near Edinburgh, in
OL,10,Fwhat was described as a "powerful
OL,11,Fsymbol of unity, service and pride".
OL,13,FOther events are planned for the
OL,14,Fweekend across service communities,
OL,15,Fincluding a public parade, "muster
OL,16,Fmarch" and an act of remembrance in
OL,17,FEdinburgh, which will bring together
OL,18,Fserving personnel, veterans and
OL,19,Ffamilies from across Scotland.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@VO]rD@YOUsD@cO]wD@\OUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
