FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FFurther events are due to take place
OL,7,Fthroughout the year, and a new
OL,8,Fcommemorative sculpture in Princes
OL,9,FStreet Gardens in Edinburgh is set to
OL,10,Fbe unveiled on July 1.
OL,12,FThe design will feature a bronze
OL,13,Freclining lion guarding the SCOTS cap
OL,14,Fbadge, symbolising the regiment's
OL,15,Fenduring connection to Edinburgh and
OL,16,Fcreating a place for reflection for
OL,17,Ffuture generations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
