FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FLieutenant Colonel Ollie Bridle, who
OL,7,Fcommands the 2nd Battalion, The Royal
OL,8,FRegiment of Scotland (2 SCOTS), said:
OL,9,F"We're proud to be marking 20 years of
OL,10,FThe Royal Regiment of Scotland.
OL,12,F"Over that time, the regiment has
OL,13,Fbrought together generations of
OL,14,Fsoldiers, united by a shared identity,
OL,15,Fheritage and sense of service, all
OL,16,Funder one cap badge."
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FThe decision to amalgamate six
OL,7,Fhistoric regiments was considered
OL,8,Fcontroversial at the time, and the
OL,9,Fgovernment faced calls to reverse the
OL,10,Fmove.
OL,12,FThis included the campaign group Save
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Regiments holding marches
OL,14,Fand rallies to voice its opposition,
OL,15,Fwarning of a loss of tradition and
OL,16,Flocal identity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FHowever, many of the traditions of the
OL,7,Fold formations were retained when the
OL,8,FRoyal Regiment of Scotland was formed,
OL,9,Fwith its predecessor regiments
OL,10,Fbecoming battalions in the new
OL,11,Fregiment.
OL,13,FThree of the battalions also maintain
OL,14,Fthe pipes and drums of their former
OL,15,Fregiments.
OL,17,FLt Col Bridle continued: "We were
OL,18,Ffounded on the legacy of historic
OL,19,FScottish infantry regiments,
OL,20,Frepresenting over 390 years of
OL,21,Fcontinuous service.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,F"Today, we stand as one regiment with
OL,7,Fa clear identity and purpose.
OL,9,F"SCOTS soldiers are tough. They're
OL,10,Fstrong. They've got that sense of
OL,11,Fhumour that you need on the hardest
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,F"They face problems head-on and when
OL,15,Fit's done, they move forward and don't
OL,16,Flook back.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,F"This anniversary is about recognising
OL,7,Feveryone who has served with us, our
OL,8,Fveterans, our fallen, and those
OL,9,Fserving today, whether at home or
OL,10,Foverseas.
OL,12,F"It's also about looking ahead to the
OL,13,Fnext generation and the important role
OL,14,Fthat SCOTS soldiers will continue to
OL,15,Fplay in the years to come."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
