PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774663388
OL,3,CRoyal Regiment of Scotland to
OL,4,Ccelebrate 20th anniversary
OL,6,FThe Royal Regiment of Scotland was
OL,7,Fformed in 2006 from an amalgamation of
OL,8,FThe Royal Scots, the King's Own
OL,9,FScottish Borderers, the Royal Highland
OL,10,FFusiliers, The Black Watch, The
OL,11,FHighlanders, and the Argyll and
OL,12,FSutherland Highlanders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
